Company's manager should be UAE-resident OR should have visa under RAKEZ within six (6) months from the date of registration if he he/she has no UAE visa. 4. Company's Manager should have the minimal qualifications required such as bachelor degree in Business Administration or Economics or a related discipline and three years experience. 5. Undertaking not to act as a Corporate Service Provider (CSP) for the below services: • Acting as a formation agent of legal persons • Acting as (or arranging for another person to act as) a director or secretary of a company, a partner of a partnership, or a similar position in relation to other legal persons. • Providing a registered office; business address or accommodation, correspondence or administrative address for a company, a partnership or any other legal person or arrangement. • Acting as (or arranging for another person to act as) a trustee of an express trust. • Acting as (or arranging for another person to act as) a nominee shareholder for another person.

Description: Web/mobile platform, which aggregates the listings of third parties (i.e. not the web/mobile platform owners’ own goods or services). A content rich software application/website which aggregates a variety of information and content (e.g. text, photos, graphics, videos etc.) about a specific subject matter or for a specific purpose to make the content accessible to the public in a clear, easy and organized way. Typically there is a subscription element, which may be with or without a subscription fee. In app purchases may be permitted, but this is incidental to the core purpose of the app/website. The app/website is not supporting a physical business; it is an independent business in itself, solely operating through the app/website.

Description: Web/mobile e-commerce platform that allows a customer to search, book and pay for an activity or service provided by a third party. The activity/service is paid for directly through the platform (i.e. payment is taken by the platform itself not the third party service provider) and typically the platform will make a commission from each booking

Activity Name (Arabic): بوابة محتوى - منصة مقارنات عبر الإنترنت
Description: Web/mobile based price analysis tool that allows a customer to use an online search engine to find and compare products and/or services using selected criteria e.g. price, features, reviews, ratings etc. The platform aggregates listings of products and/or services from different retailers but does not directly sell the products itself. The platform typically does not have the functionality to make in-platform purchases (i.e. there is no payment gateway) but instead links the customer with the third party retailer. Comparison tools for higher risk products e.g. medical products, insurance, car loans, mortgages etc. would generally not be acceptable as providing advice in relation to these products may be regulated (e.g. by Ministry of Health).

Business Plan to be Reviewed and Approved by Sales Director, Ministry of Health & Prevention, Department of Civil Defence, General Resources Authority-CCTV. Guidelines on how to obtain the required NOC from MOHAP to conduct such business: 1. Facility must be Warehouse/Land 2. International & local Marketing Authorization holders are allowed to operate within the UAE and register themselves as scientific offices with MOHAP. 3. All scientific offices are allowed to apply for registration, manage all their post marketing surveillance in the country, appoint local agents & issue invoices with the required authorization from the principal company. 4. A principal company/ Marketing Authorization Holder is recognized by MOHAP through the registration of their products. The registration certificate of any medical product/drug marketed within the UAE specifies the Marketing Authorization Holder, the Manufacturer & the local agent. 5. Scientific Offices are also eligible to request for a logistic storage hub, i.e. apply for a Good Storage Practice (GSP) certificate for logistic stores . 6. if the applicants for medical trading activity do represent the MAH (marketing authorization holder) of related medical product as distributors with relevant official agreements, GSP certificate from MOHAP can be issued after inspection and fulfilling the requirements accurately. Accordingly, they can practice such activities, otherwise, they are not eligible. 'Mandatory RAKEZ Visa within 6 months of the License Issuance".

Documents Required: 1. Standalone License with ""Management Consultancy” activity. If any additional activities are required, Client should have additional license subject to satisfying the relevant requirements. 2. Special Activity Fee AED 6,500/- to be charged for New Registration and Amendment Activity (Existing Clients) Cases 3. Company's manager should be UAE-resident OR should have visa under RAKEZ within six (6) months from the date of registration if he he/she has no UAE visa. 4. Company's Manager should have the minimal qualifications required such as bachelor degree in Business Administration or Economics or a related discipline and three years experience. 5. Undertaking not to act as a Corporate Service Provider (CSP) for the below services: • Acting as a formation agent of legal persons • Acting as (or arranging for another person to act as) a director or secretary of a company, a partner of a partnership, or a similar position in relation to other legal persons. • Providing a registered office; business address or accommodation, correspondence or administrative address for a company, a partnership or any other legal person or arrangement. • Acting as (or arranging for another person to act as) a trustee of an express trust. • Acting as (or arranging for another person to act as) a nominee shareholder for another person.

Description: Includes reselling of certain instruments and precise medical apparatuses for treating of certain diseases, such as earphones, batteries for cardiac patients, pulse regulators, walking-sticks, splints for bone fractures, medical shoes, artificial limbs, dentures and other medical instruments, also, surgical requisites like artificial organs and parts to replace damaged organs, bone joints, heart valves, in additional to surgical suture bandages and plasters .
Description (Arabic): هي إعادة بيع بعض الأدوات والأجهزة الطبية الدقيقة التي تستخدم في علاج بعض الأمراض كسماعات الأذن للصم والبطاريات ومنظمات النبض لمرضى القلب  والعكاكيز والجبائر للمصابين بكسور في العظام والأحذية الطبية، والأجهزة التعويضية وأطقم الأسنان وكذلك الأدوات التي تعمل بواسطة التأثير المغناطيسي وغيرها من الأدوات الطبية العلاجية كما يشمل هذا النشاط إعادة بيع المستلزمات الجراحية كالأعضاء أو الأجزاء الاصطناعية التي يجرى استبدالها بالأجزاء التالفة مثل مفاصل العظام أو صمامات القلب أو غيرها، بالإضافة إلى خيوط الجرا
Documents Required: Business Plan to be Reviewed and Approved by Sales Director. Ministry of Health & Prevention. For Warehouse & Land: Department of Civil Defense, General Resources Authority-CCTV. Guidelines on how to obtain the required NOC from MOHAP to conduct such business: 1. Facility must be dedicated Office/Warehouse/Land 2. International & local Marketing Authorization holders are allowed to operate within the UAE and register themselves as scientific offices with MOHAP. 3. All scientific offices are allowed to apply for registration, manage all their post marketing surveillance in the country, appoint local agents & issue invoices with the required authorization from the principal company. 4. A principal company/ Marketing Authorization Holder is recognized by MOHAP through the registration of their products. The registration certificate of any medical product/drug marketed within the UAE specifies the Marketing Authorization Holder, the Manufacturer & the local agent. 5. Scientific Offices are also eligible to request for a logistic storage hub, i.e. apply for a Good Storage Practice (GSP) certificate for logistic stores . 6. if the applicants for medical trading activity do represent the MAH (marketing authorization holder) of related medical product as distributors with relevant official agreements, GSP certificate from MOHAP can be issued after inspection and fulfilling the requirements accurately. Accordingly, they can practice such activities, otherwise, they are not eligible.'Mandatory RAKEZ Visa within 6 months of the License Issuance".

Guidelines on how to obtain the required NOC from MOHAP to conduct such business: 1. Facility must be dedicated Office/Warehouse/Land 2. International & local Marketing Authorization holders are allowed to operate within the UAE and register themselves as scientific offices with MOHAP. 3. All scientific offices are allowed to apply for registration, manage all their post marketing surveillance in the country, appoint local agents & issue invoices with the required authorization from the principal company. 4. A principal company/ Marketing Authorization Holder is recognized by MOHAP through the registration of their products. The registration certificate of any medical product/drug marketed within the UAE specifies the Marketing Authorization Holder, the Manufacturer & the local agent. 5. Scientific Offices are also eligible to request for a logistic storage hub, i.e. apply for a Good Storage Practice (GSP) certificate for logistic stores . 6. if the applicants for medical trading activity do represent the MAH (marketing authorization holder) of related medical product as distributors with relevant official agreements, GSP certificate from MOHAP can be issued after inspection and fulfilling the requirements accurately. Accordingly, they can practice such activities, otherwise, they are not eligible.'Mandatory RAKEZ Visa within 6 months of the License Issuance".

Documents Required: Business Plan to be Reviewed and Approved by Sales Director. Ministry of Health & Prevention. For Warehouse & Land: Department of Civil Defense, General Resources Authority-CCTV. Guidelines on how to obtain the required NOC from MOHAP to conduct such business: 1. Facility must be dedicated Office/Warehouse/Land 2. International & local Marketing Authorization holders are allowed to operate within the UAE and register themselves as scientific offices with MOHAP. 3. All scientific offices are allowed to apply for registration, manage all their post marketing surveillance in the country, appoint local agents & issue invoices with the required authorization from the principal company. 4. A principal company/ Marketing Authorization Holder is recognized by MOHAP through the registration of their products. The registration certificate of any medical product/drug marketed within the UAE specifies the Marketing Authorization Holder, the Manufacturer & the local agent. 5. Scientific Offices are also eligible to request for a logistic storage hub, i.e. apply for a Good Storage Practice (GSP) certificate for logistic stores . 6. if the applicants for medical trading activity do represent the MAH (marketing authorization holder) of related medical product as distributors with relevant official agreements, GSP certificate from MOHAP can be issued after inspection and fulfilling the requirements accurately. Accordingly, they can practice such activities, otherwise, they are not eligible.

Documents Required: Business Plan to be Reviewed and Approved by Sales Director. Ministry of Health & Prevention. For Warehouse & Land: Department of Civil Defense, General Resources Authority-CCTV. Guidelines on how to obtain the required NOC from MOHAP to conduct such business: 1. Facility must be dedicated Office/Warehouse/Land 2. International & local Marketing Authorization holders are allowed to operate within the UAE and register themselves as scientific offices with MOHAP. 3. All scientific offices are allowed to apply for registration, manage all their post marketing surveillance in the country, appoint local agents & issue invoices with the required authorization from the principal company. 4. A principal company/ Marketing Authorization Holder is recognized by MOHAP through the registration of their products. The registration certificate of any medical product/drug marketed within the UAE specifies the Marketing Authorization Holder, the Manufacturer & the local agent. 5. Scientific Offices are also eligible to request for a logistic storage hub, i.e. apply for a Good Storage Practice (GSP) certificate for logistic stores . 6. if the applicants for medical trading activity do represent the MAH (marketing authorization holder) of related medical product as distributors with relevant official agreements, GSP certificate from MOHAP can be issued after inspection and fulfilling the requirements accurately. Accordingly, they can practice such activities, otherwise, they are not eligible.'Mandatory RAKEZ Visa within 6 months of the License Issuance".

Activity Name: Trade equipment and medical devices - wholesale
Documents Required: Business Plan to be Reviewed and Approved by Sales Director. Ministry of Health & Prevention. For Warehouse & Land: Department of Civil Defense, General Resources Authority-CCTV. Guidelines on how to obtain the required NOC from MOHAP to conduct such business: 1. Facility must be dedicated Office/Warehouse/Land 2. International & local Marketing Authorization holders are allowed to operate within the UAE and register themselves as scientific offices with MOHAP. 3. All scientific offices are allowed to apply for registration, manage all their post marketing surveillance in the country, appoint local agents & issue invoices with the required authorization from the principal company. 4. A principal company/ Marketing Authorization Holder is recognized by MOHAP through the registration of their products. The registration certificate of any medical product/drug marketed within the UAE specifies the Marketing Authorization Holder, the Manufacturer & the local agent. 5. Scientific Offices are also eligible to request for a logistic storage hub, i.e. apply for a Good Storage Practice (GSP) certificate for logistic stores . 6. if the applicants for medical trading activity do represent the MAH (marketing authorization holder) of related medical product as distributors with relevant official agreements, GSP certificate from MOHAP can be issued after inspection and fulfilling the requirements accurately. Accordingly, they can practice such activities, otherwise, they are not eligible.

Documents Required: Business Plan to be Reviewed and Approved by Sales Director. Ministry of Health & Prevention. For Warehouse & Land: Department of Civil Defense, General Resources Authority-CCTV. Guidelines on how to obtain the required NOC from MOHAP to conduct such business: 1. Facility must be dedicated Office/Warehouse/Land 2. International & local Marketing Authorization holders are allowed to operate within the UAE and register themselves as scientific offices with MOHAP. 3. All scientific offices are allowed to apply for registration, manage all their post marketing surveillance in the country, appoint local agents & issue invoices with the required authorization from the principal company. 4. A principal company/ Marketing Authorization Holder is recognized by MOHAP through the registration of their products. The registration certificate of any medical product/drug marketed within the UAE specifies the Marketing Authorization Holder, the Manufacturer & the local agent. 5. Scientific Offices are also eligible to request for a logistic storage hub, i.e. apply for a Good Storage Practice (GSP) certificate for logistic stores . 6. if the applicants for medical trading activity do represent the MAH (marketing authorization holder) of related medical product as distributors with relevant official agreements, GSP certificate from MOHAP can be issued after inspection and fulfilling the requirements accurately. Accordingly, they can practice such activities, otherwise, they are not eligible.
